snippet.title: Ancient Amuletor - Announce Trailer | PS VR
snippet.description:
Imagine yourself as a mage, archer, or gunslinger in the ancient world; use your special skill to defend against waves of enemies.  

PlayStation VR and two PlayStation Move Controllers are required to play.
